      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنِ اَلرَّجُلِ يَعْتَمِرُ عُمْرَةً مُفْرَدَةً فَقَالَ «إِذَا رَأَيْتَ ذَا طُوًى فَاقْطَعِ اَلتَّلْبِيَةَ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2956 - It was narrated from Yunus ibn Ya'qub, who said:\nI asked Abu Abdullah (as) about a man performing an independent Umrah Mufradah.\nImam (as) said: \"When you see Dhu Tuwa, stop the Talbiyah.\""
        ]
      }
